<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Craiseek · Real-Time Craigslist Rental Radar</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Roboto+Mono:wght@500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #2563eb;
            --primary-dark: #1e3a8a;
            --bg: #0f172a;
            --text: #0f172a;
            --muted: #475569;
            --surface: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
        }
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(59,130,246,0.25), transparent 40%),
                        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(14,165,233,0.2), transparent 45%),
                        #f8fafc;
            color: var(--text);
        }
        header {
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 10;
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            background-color: rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.9);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.2);
        }
        .nav {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px 24px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        .brand {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            color: var(--primary);
        }
        .brand span {
            display: inline-flex;
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), #38bdf8);
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        nav a, nav button {
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-left: 18px;
            color: var(--muted);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.2s ease;
        }
        nav button {
            background: none;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            padding: 0;
        }
        nav a:hover, nav button:hover {
            color: var(--primary);
        }
        main {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px 24px 96px;
        }
        .hero {
            position: relative;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(37,99,235,0.15), rgba(14,165,233,0.05));
            border-radius: 28px;
            padding: 64px 56px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12);
        }
        .hero::before, .hero::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            width: 240px;
            height: 240px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            filter: blur(80px);
            opacity: 0.4;
            animation: pulse 18s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
        }
        .hero::before {
            background: rgba(59,130,246,0.6);
            top: -120px;
            left: -80px;
        }
        .hero::after {
            background: rgba(14,165,233,0.55);
            bottom: -120px;
            right: -80px;
            animation-delay: 2s;
        }
        .hero-content {
            max-width: 540px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.12);
            color: var(--primary);
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin: 0 0 18px;
            line-height: 1.1;
            animation: slideUp 0.8s ease;
        }
        .hero p {
            margin: 0 0 28px;
            color: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.75);
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .hero-actions {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 16px;
        }
        .cta-primary, .cta-secondary {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
        }
        .cta-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), #38bdf8);
            color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 16px 30px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.35);
        }
        .cta-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 22px 40px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.35);
        }
        .cta-secondary {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
            color: var(--primary);
            border: 1px solid rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.2);
        }
        .cta-secondary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            border-color: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.35);
        }
        .hero-metrics {
            position: absolute;
            right: 48px;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            display: grid;
            gap: 18px;
            min-width: 220px;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .metric-card {
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.8);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 18px 20px;
            border-radius: 18px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.2);
            animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        .metric-card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 1s; }
        .metric-card:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 2s; }
        .metric-card h3 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 2rem;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }
        .metric-card span {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            opacity: 0.75;
        }
        .section {
            margin-top: 96px;
        }
        .section-header {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 640px;
            margin: 0 auto 48px;
        }
        .section-header h2 {
            font-size: 2.4rem;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .section-header p {
            color: var(--muted);
            margin: 0;
        }
        .feature-grid {
            display: grid;
            gap: 24px;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
        }
        .feature-card {
            padding: 26px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
            transform: translateY(24px);
            opacity: 0;
            transition: transform 0.6s ease, opacity 0.6s ease;
        }
        .feature-card.visible {
            transform: translateY(0);
            opacity: 1;
        }
        .feature-card h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-size: 1.35rem;
        }
        .feature-card p {
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--muted);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .latest-listings {
            display: grid;
            gap: 20px;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
        }
        .listing {
            border-radius: 18px;
            padding: 22px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.94), rgba(241,245,249,0.9));
            box-shadow: 0 18px 36px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.1);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .listing::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: -40px;
            right: -40px;
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(37,99,235,0.08);
        }
        .listing h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .listing .meta {
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            color: var(--muted);
            font-family: 'Roboto Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        .listing a {
            color: var(--primary);
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .neighborhoods {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 12px;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .neighborhood {
            padding: 10px 18px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.12);
            color: var(--primary);
            font-weight: 600;
            animation: fadeIn 0.7s ease both;
        }
        .testimonial {
            max-width: 720px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 48px;
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.92);
            color: #f8fafc;
            border-radius: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.25);
            position: relative;
        }
        .testimonial::before {
            content: "“";
            position: absolute;
            top: -40px;
            left: 32px;
            font-size: 6rem;
            color: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.15);
        }
        .testimonial p {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        .testimonial span {
            display: block;
            margin-top: 24px;
            color: rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.7);
        }
        .final-cta {
            margin-top: 96px;
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(120deg, rgba(37,99,235,0.16), rgba(59,130,246,0.1));
            padding: 48px 24px;
            border-radius: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 26px 50px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.15);
        }
        .final-cta h2 {
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 2.3rem;
        }
        .final-cta p {
            color: var(--muted);
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        footer {
            margin-top: 96px;
            padding: 32px 24px;
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--muted);
        }
        @keyframes slideUp {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
        @keyframes pulse {
            from { transform: scale(0.9); opacity: 0.35; }
            to { transform: scale(1.1); opacity: 0.55; }
        }
        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
        }
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            .hero {
                padding: 56px 40px;
            }
            .hero-metrics {
                position: static;
                transform: none;
                margin-top: 32px;
                grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            }
        }
        @media (max-width: 720px) {
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 2.4rem;
            }
            .hero {
                padding: 48px 32px;
            }
            .hero-actions {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: stretch;
            }
            .nav {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 12px;
            }
            nav a, nav button {
                margin-left: 12px;
            }
            .testimonial {
                padding: 36px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<header>
    <div class="nav">
        <div class="brand"><span>C</span> Craiseek</div>
        <nav>
            <a href="/subscribe">Plans</a>
            <a href="#features">Experience</a>
            <a href="#listings">Live Feed</a>
            <a href="#testimonial">Trust</a>
            {% if user %}
                <a href="/dashboard">Dashboard</a>
                <form action="/logout" method="post" style="display:inline;">
                    <button type="submit">Log out</button>
                </form>
            {% else %}
                <a href="/register">Register</a>
                <a href="/login">Log in</a>
            {% endif %}
        </nav>
    </div>
</header>
<main>
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <div class="badge">Real-time rental intel · SMS fast lane</div>
            <h1>Your competitors see good rentals hours later. You see them instantly.</h1>
            <p>Join the renters who hear about hot Craigslist listings before they trend. We refresh every few minutes, keep your inbox prioritized, and text you what matters.</p>
            <div class="hero-actions">
                <a class="cta-primary" href="/subscribe">Explore plans & pricing</a>
                <a class="cta-secondary" href="/dashboard">Preview the dashboard →</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-metrics">
            <div class="metric-card">
                <h3>{{ listing_count }}</h3>
                <span>Listings tracked</span>
            </div>
            <div class="metric-card">
                <h3>{{ subscriber_count }}</h3>
                <span>Hungry renters onboard</span>
            </div>
            <div class="metric-card">
                <h3>{{ fomo_remaining }}</h3>
                <span>Spots left this month</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="features">
        <div class="section-header">
            <h2>Why renters love Craiseek</h2>
            <p>Purpose-built for speed, clarity, and an unfair advantage in crowded rental markets.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-grid">
            <article class="feature-card fade">
                <h3>Lightning scrapes</h3>
                <p>We hit Craigslist every five minutes with smart backoff so you never get blocked, then surface fresh posts instantly.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="feature-card fade">
                <h3>Precision alerts</h3>
                <p>Texts include price, neighborhood, and direct links. No duplicates, no noise&mdash;just actionable leads.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="feature-card fade">
                <h3>Actionable dashboard</h3>
                <p>Even without SMS, scan our real-time dashboard for trends, neighborhoods, and rates that match your search.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="feature-card fade">
                <h3>Payment-ready</h3>
                <p>Secure Stripe checkout collects your phone number and gets alerts flowing immediately.</p>
            </article>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="listings">
        <div class="section-header">
            <h2>Fresh out of the feed</h2>
            <p>Here&#39;s a glimpse of what subscribers are seeing in real time.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="latest-listings">
            {% for listing in latest_listings %}
                <article class="listing fade">
                    <h3>{{ listing.title }}</h3>
                    <div class="meta">
                        {% if listing.price %}<span>{{ listing.price }}</span>{% endif %}
                        {% if listing.neighborhood %}<span>{{ listing.neighborhood }}</span>{% endif %}
                    </div>
                    <a href="{{ listing.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">View on Craigslist →</a>
                </article>
            {% else %}
                <article class="listing fade">
                    <h3>No listings yet</h3>
                    <p>We haven&#39;t tracked any posts yet. Once the scraper runs, you&#39;ll see listings populate here instantly.</p>
                </article>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
        {% if neighborhoods %}
            <div class="section-header" style="margin-top: 56px;">
                <h2>Neighborhood heat radar</h2>
                <p>Listings spotted most recently across the city.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="neighborhoods">
                {% for hood in neighborhoods %}
                    <span class="neighborhood">{{ hood }}</span>
                {% endfor %}
            </div>
        {% endif %}
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="testimonial">
        <div class="section-header">
            <h2>Trusted by renters chasing the edge</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial fade">
            <p>&ldquo;Craiseek gave me a two-hour head start on a dream loft in Hayes Valley. By the time other renters showed up, I was already signing paperwork. The texts are snappy, relevant, and worth every dollar.&rdquo;</p>
            <span>&mdash; Maya, San Francisco renter</span>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="final-cta fade">
        <h2>Claims go fast. Your alert should go faster.</h2>
        <p>Reserve one of the last {{ fomo_remaining }} subscriber slots and unlock real-time rental intelligence today.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions" style="justify-content:center;">
            <a class="cta-primary" href="/subscribe">Choose your alert style</a>
            <a class="cta-secondary" href="/register">Create free dashboard account</a>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>
<footer>
    © 2025 Craiseek · Built by rental hunters for renters.
</footer>
<script>
    const observer = new IntersectionObserver(entries => {
        entries.forEach(entry => {
            if (entry.isIntersecting) {
                entry.target.classList.add('visible');
                observer.unobserve(entry.target);
            }
        });
    }, { threshold: 0.2 });

    document.querySelectorAll('.fade, .listing').forEach(el => observer.observe(el));
</script>
</body>
</html>
